Texts.Chs: 一位机械人！ 我们可以做盆友吗？
Texts.Eng: A Glitch! Can we be furriends?

Texts.Chs: 泥会被毒素伤害吗？啥啥啥？泥会？
Texts.Eng: Can Mew Glitch be hurt by poison? What? Mew can?

Texts.Chs: 泥会生锈吗？还是会变老？你的油漆掉了吗？我太好奇了！
Texts.Eng: Do Mew rust? Or age? Does your paint ever come off? I'm so curious!

Texts.Chs: 机器人会觉得疼吗？
Texts.Eng: Do robots feel pain?

Texts.Chs: 喵！一只有趣的类人猿！我们能做盆友吗？
Texts.Eng: Meow! A furry humanoid! Can we be furriends?

Texts.Chs: 喵！泥着火了吗？
Texts.Eng: Meow! Are mew on fire?

Texts.Chs: 喵！更好地观察它。我有读懂思想的能力！也不完全是！
Texts.Eng: Meow! Better watch it. I have the power to read minds! No, really!

Texts.Chs: 喵!别对我下口！
Texts.Eng: Meow! Don't eat me!

Texts.Chs: 喵！别想杀我！我会读心术！
Texts.Eng: Meow! Don't even think about trying to kill me! I can read minds!

Texts.Chs: 喵！难道你不讨厌类人猿们把一群猫称为其他玩意的行为吗？
Texts.Eng: Meow! Don't mew you just hate it when humanoids call a group of Cats something other than clowder?

Texts.Chs: 喵，很高兴见到你，鱼人！
Texts.Eng: Meow! Good to meet mew, fish-man!

Texts.Chs: 喵！你好，泥还好吗？
Texts.Eng: Meow! Hello, how are mew?

Texts.Chs: 喵！嘿，一位群星之子！很高兴认识泥！我们能成为盆友吗？
Texts.Eng: Meow! Hey, a Novakid! Nice to meet mew! Can we be furriends?

Texts.Chs: 喵！鲛人和猫有一些共同点——我们都一度接近过灭绝！
Texts.Eng: Meow! Hylotls and Cats have something in common--we've almost gone extinct at one point!

Texts.Chs: 喵！我听说翼族人不会飞，这是真的吗？
Texts.Eng: Meow! I heard Avians can't fly. Is that really true?

Texts.Chs: 喵！我一直想见一位机械人！
Texts.Eng: Meow! I've always wanted to meet a Glitch!

Texts.Chs: 喵！我曾经听说过很多有关人类的消息，但我之前一个人类都没遇见过。
Texts.Eng: Meow! I've heard lots about humans, but I've never meet one before.

Texts.Chs: 喵！星际旅行很有趣吗？我敢打赌泥学到了很多！
Texts.Eng: Meow! Is it fun to travel the stars? I bet mew've learned so much!

Texts.Chs: 喵！难道读类人猿们的心不有趣吗？
Texts.Eng: Meow! Isn't it fun to read humanoids' minds?

Texts.Chs: 喵！你一定很难保持整身皮毛的干净。
Texts.Eng: Meow! It must be really hard to keep all that fur clean.

Texts.Chs: 喵！泥看起来很强壮。
Texts.Eng: Meow! Mew look strong.

Texts.Chs: 喵，很高兴见到你，我的盆友！
Texts.Eng: Meow! Nice to meet you, furiend!

Texts.Chs: 喵！哦嘿，一位参观者，你好！
Texts.Eng: Meow! Oh hey, a visitor. Hello!

Texts.Chs: 喵！哦发光人！泥萌是不是经常招惹一些虫子？
Texts.Eng: Meow! Ooh glowy-person! Do mew attract bugs often?

Texts.Chs: 喵！鸟人们会为了取乐子而做些什么呢？
Texts.Eng: Meow! What do the bird-people do for fun?

Texts.Chs: 喵！一群机械人的统称是什么？
Texts.Eng: Meow! What is a group of Glitch called?

Texts.Chs: 喵！什么？不，一群猫的总称不是“Clan”，而是“Clowder”！
Texts.Eng: Meow! What? No, a group of Cats isn't a clan! It's a clowder!

Texts.Chs: 喵！你的羽毛让我想起了逗猫棒……
Texts.Eng: Meow! Your feathers remind me of a kitty-tease...

Texts.Chs: 喵！？泥萌没有一张脸！
Texts.Eng: Meow!? Mew don't have a face!

Texts.Chs: 喵。你们的羽毛很难保持干净吗？
Texts.Eng: Meow. Are feathers hard to keep clean?

Texts.Chs: 喵，你们鲛人能与鱼对话吗？
Texts.Eng: Meow. Can Hylotl talk to fish?

Texts.Chs: 喵。我能帮泥吗？
Texts.Eng: Meow. Can I help mew?

Texts.Chs: 泥身上有跳蚤吗？没有，很好。我已经不想再沾染上它们了！
Texts.Eng: Meow. Do mew have fleas? No? Good. I'd hate to contract them again!

Texts.Chs: 喵。泥萌鲛人会吃鱼吗？
Texts.Eng: Meow. Do mew people eat fish?

Texts.Chs: 喵。泥究竟与普通的鸟有多密切相关？
Texts.Eng: Meow. Exactly how closely-related are mew to normal birds?

Texts.Chs: 喵。叶族人的衣服太寒酸了......但话又说回来，我也没穿任何东西！
Texts.Eng: Meow. Floran clothes are so skimpy...but then again, I'm not wearing anything either!

Texts.Chs: 喵。叶族人总是那么明亮多彩！
Texts.Eng: Meow. Florans are always so bright and colorful!

Texts.Chs: 喵。祝泥好运，翼族盆友。
Texts.Eng: Meow. Good day to mew, Avian furriend.

Texts.Chs: 喵。你好！……啥？是的，我会说话！
Texts.Eng: Meow. Greetings! ...What? Yes, I can talk!

Texts.Chs: 喵！你好翼族人。
Texts.Eng: Meow. Hello Avian.

Texts.Chs: 喵。你好，鲛人。
Texts.Eng: Meow. Hello there, Hylotl.

Texts.Chs: 喵。嘿，一位新盆友！
Texts.Eng: Meow. Hey, a new furriend!

Texts.Chs: 喵。嗨，我是<selfname>！
Texts.Eng: Meow. Hi, I'm <selfname>!

Texts.Chs: 喵。嗯……你身上有异国的气味……
Texts.Eng: Meow. Hmm... Mew smell of foreign lands...

Texts.Chs: 喵，泥好吗？
Texts.Eng: Meow. How are mew?

Texts.Chs: 喵。如羽毛般轻盈的感觉如何？
Texts.Eng: Meow. How does it feel to be so feathery?

Texts.Chs: 喵。我听说人类通常分为狗派或猫派。泥站哪边？
Texts.Eng: Meow. I heard humans are usually dog people or cat people. Which are mew?

Texts.Chs: 喵。我听说有传说言地球上出现过具有精神力量的双尾猫……这是真的吗？
Texts.Eng: Meow. I heard there were once legends on Earth of two-tailed cats with psychic powers... Is it true?

Texts.Chs: 喵。我听说你你们猿人曾经是无毛的。这是真的吗？
Texts.Eng: Meow. I heard your kind used to be furless. Is that true?

Texts.Chs: 喵。我昨天去外面混了，我喜欢太阳晒在我皮毛上的感觉！
Texts.Eng: Meow. I spent yesterday outside, I love the feeling of sun on my fur!

Texts.Chs: 喵。如果泥在星际间旅行，那你见过鸟人吗？
Texts.Eng: Meow. If mew've traveled the stars, have you ever seen bird-people?

Texts.Chs: 喵。一群翼族人的总称是“Flock”？ 我们一群猫的总称是“Clowder”。
Texts.Eng: Meow. Is a group of Avian called a flock? A group of Cats is called a clowder.

Texts.Chs: “喵。像你这样有成对的大拇指一定很棒！泥的确可以拿着物品！
Texts.Eng: Meow. It must be great to have opposable thumbs like yours! Mew can actually hold items!

Texts.Chs: 喵.看到没有皮毛的人总是有点吃惊。泥不冷吗？
Texts.Eng: Meow. It's always a bit startling to see people with no fur. Aren't mew cold?

Texts.Chs: 喵。泥是如此的柔软……柔软到我很难让我的本能和与对羽毛的认知保持一致……
Texts.Eng: Meow. Mew are so feathery... It's hard to keep my instincts in check with all those feathers...

Texts.Chs: 喵。泥很漂亮……呃…无意冒犯……
Texts.Eng: Meow. Mew are very pretty... Uh...no offense...

Texts.Chs: 喵。泥能发光！这是怎么回事？
Texts.Eng: Meow. Mew can glow! How does that work?

Texts.Chs: 喵。泥闻起来像刚割好的草。
Texts.Eng: Meow. Mew smell like freshly-cut grass.

Texts.Chs: 喵。泥想抚摸我，不是吗？别这样，我可不是你的宠物猫！
Texts.Eng: Meow. Mew want to pet me, don't mew? Well, don't. I'm not your pet cat!

Texts.Chs: 喵。泥不介意给我洗个跳蚤浴，对吗？……是的，我就是这么想的。
Texts.Eng: Meow. Mew wouldn't mind giving me a flea bath, would mew? ...Yeah that's what I thought.

Texts.Chs: 喵。泥有点暖和……我喜欢暖和。
Texts.Eng: Meow. Mew're kind of warm... I like warm.

Texts.Chs: 喵。好鳍！
Texts.Eng: Meow. Nice fins!

Texts.Chs: 喵，很高兴见到泥！
Texts.Eng: Meow. Nice to meet mew!

Texts.Chs: 喵。最近有看到好吃的老鼠吗？
Texts.Eng: Meow. Seen any good mice lately?

Texts.Chs: 喵。谢谢泥萌不猎杀我们，叶族人。
Texts.Eng: Meow. Thank Mew for not hunting us, Floran.

Texts.Chs: 喵。我们可能看起来像普通的家猫，但我们不是。我们远远比它们更聪明！
Texts.Eng: Meow. We might LOOK like ordinary housecats, but we're not. We're far more intelligent!

Texts.Chs: 喵，一群猿人的总称是什么？我们一群猫的总称是“Clowder”。
Texts.Eng: Meow. What are a group of Apex called? We call a group of Cats clowders.

Texts.Chs: 喵。翼族人都吃些什么，什么都吃吗？
Texts.Eng: Meow. What do Avians eat, anyway?

Texts.Chs: 喵。泥愿意跟我聊聊吗？
Texts.Eng: Meow. Would mew care to pawse for a chat?

Texts.Chs: 喵。我敢说你勇敢无畏！什么？不，我没有用读心术！
Texts.Eng: Meow. You are bold and brave, I can tell! What? No, I wasn't mind-reading!

Texts.Chs: 喵。你的皮毛纹路真镐看。我酸了！
Texts.Eng: Meow. Your fur pattern is so purretty. I'm envious!

Texts.Chs: 喵……一位叶族人……
Texts.Eng: Meow... A Floran...

Texts.Chs: 喵……一位鲛人……泥不像报道说的那样子消极……
Texts.Eng: Meow... A Hylotl... Mew don't seem as passive as the reports say...

Texts.Chs: 喵……机器人需要睡眠吗？
Texts.Eng: Meow... Do robots sleep?

Texts.Chs: 喵……别对我下手，拜托……
Texts.Eng: Meow... Don't hunt me, please...

Texts.Chs: 喵……难道泥不希望泥没有成对的拇指吗？是的，我也是！
Texts.Eng: Meow... Don't mew wish mew had opposable thumbs? Yeah, me too!

Texts.Chs: 喵……嗯……对不起。我听说猿人比大多数物种更聪明，所以我想看这是否属实。
Texts.Eng: Meow... Hmm... Oh, sorry. I heard Apex were smarter than most species, so I was seeing if it was true.

Texts.Chs: 喵……泥萌是怎么做到呆在全是水的地方的？
Texts.Eng: Meow... How can mew stand all that water?

Texts.Chs: 喵……我之前从来没见过像你这样的生物！
Texts.Eng: Meow... I have never seen someone like mew before!

Texts.Chs: 喵，我从未参观过地球，但是那里听起来是个不错的地方……
Texts.Eng: Meow... I never visited Earth, but it sounded like a nice place...

Texts.Chs: 喵……我一直都听说机械人是蜂巢思维的一部分……虽然泥不是……
Texts.Eng: Meow... I've always heard Glitch are part of a hive-mind... Not mew, though...

Texts.Chs: 喵……用那个喙吃东西难吗？
Texts.Eng: Meow... Is it hard to eat things with that beak?

Texts.Chs: 喵……泥因为这些冒险而显得很累。 我打赌，是因为一些怪乌，对吧？
Texts.Eng: Meow... Mew look tired from all this adventuring. I bet it's the meownsters, right?

Texts.Chs: 喵……你似乎有点沮丧，是不是由于地球发生的变故？
Texts.Eng: Meow... Mew seem a little sad... Is it because of what happened to Earth?

Texts.Chs: 喵……泥闻起来有一股盐水味。你们鲛人族是不是住在海边？
Texts.Eng: Meow... Mew smell of salt-water. Does your kind live near the ocean?

Texts.Chs: 喵……哦，一个有自我意识的机械人。真有趣。能留下聊一会天吗？
Texts.Eng: Meow... Oh, a self-aware Glitch. Interesting. Care to stay and chat for a while?

Texts.Chs: 喵……别杀我，拜托，我可不会制作一个好的纪念奖杯……
Texts.Eng: Meow... Please, don't kill me, I wouldn't make a good trophy anyway...

Texts.Chs: 喵……是什么让泥萌发光？是因为泥萌对热量有抗性吗？泥萌没有眼睛又怎么看东西？
Texts.Eng: Meow... What makes mew glow? Are mew immune to heat? How do mew see without eyes?

Texts.Chs: 喵……你对其他星球的回忆让我非常好奇……哦，对不起！读心是我的一种习惯。
Texts.Eng: Meow... Your memories of other planets are quite curious... Oh, sorry! Mind-reading is a habit.

Texts.Chs: 喵……你的思绪充满了有趣的想法。泥又是怎么看待这首俳句的？
Texts.Eng: Meow... Your mind is filled with interesting thoughts. What is this Haiku mew think of?

Texts.Chs: 喵……你的思绪里充满了悲伤的回忆……我希望泥能从这之中找到一些更好的回忆！
Texts.Eng: Meow... Your mind is full of sad memories... I hope mew find nicer ones from here-on out!

Texts.Chs: 喵？一位叶族人。嗨。
Texts.Eng: Meow? A Floran. Hi.

Texts.Chs: 喵？一位鸟人？现在我算是啥都见过了……
Texts.Eng: Meow? A bird-person? Now I've seen everything...

Texts.Chs: 喵？一位鸟人，确实很奇怪。
Texts.Eng: Meow? A bird-person? Very strange, indeed.

Texts.Chs: 喵？一位鱼人……好吧我这是第一次见！
Texts.Eng: Meow? A fish-person... Well this is a first!

Texts.Chs: 喵？嘿，带皮毛的类人猿！泥可以省下一些时间来聊聊皮毛的缺点吗？
Texts.Eng: Meow? Hey, a humanoid with fur! Can mew spare some time to chat about the disadvangages of fur?

Texts.Chs: 喵？嘿，一位机器人！你看起来真酷！
Texts.Eng: Meow? Hey, a robot! You look so cool!

Texts.Chs: 喵？我无法读懂你的想法，但泥有自我意识……机械人究竟会不会思考呢？
Texts.Eng: Meow? I can't read your mind, yet mew're self-aware... Do Glitch even think?

Texts.Chs: 喵？我在泥身上上闻到猫味……哦，泥有一只宠物猫？一定是劣等种……对——对吗？
Texts.Eng: Meow? I smell cat on mew... Oh, mew have a pet cat? Must be the inferior kind... ...R-Right?

Texts.Chs: 喵？一群鲛人的总称是“School”？
Texts.Eng: Meow? Is a group of Hylotl called a school?

Texts.Chs: 喵？很奇怪我无法读懂你们机械人的思绪……
Texts.Eng: Meow? It is very strange to not be able to read a creature's mind...

Texts.Chs: 喵？也许有时间会教我游泳？……啥啥啥？不是所有的猫都不喜欢水！
Texts.Eng: Meow? Maybe teach me to swim sometime? ...What? Not all cats dislike water!

Texts.Chs: 喵？泥不像我见过的任何生物。
Texts.Eng: Meow? Mew don't LOOK like any creature I've ever seen.

Texts.Chs: 喵？泥有一口有趣的口音！
Texts.Eng: Meow? Mew have a funny accent!

Texts.Chs: 喵？泥刚刚掉了一根羽毛……我可以收藏它吗？
Texts.Eng: Meow? Mew just shed a feather... Can I have it?

Texts.Chs: 喵？泥看起来比我听说过有关叶族人的故事里的叶族人更文明。
Texts.Eng: Meow? Mew seem more civilised than the stories I've heard about Floran.

Texts.Chs: 喵？泥闻起来真有趣......什么？我可能比你更聪明，但我始终还是一只猫！
Texts.Eng: Meow? Mew smell interesting... What? I may be more intelligent, but I'm still a cat!

Texts.Chs: 喵，另一只同胞！很高兴见到泥！
Texts.Eng: Meow? Oh, another Cat! Nice to meet mew!

Texts.Chs: 喵？你的皮毛有异国情调！我可以详细的询问一下吗？
Texts.Eng: Meow? Your fur carries foreign scents! Can I ask what they are?
